VALUES ('High-Fashion Black Elegance Photo Collage Prompt', 'A detailed prompt for generating a vertical fashion collage featuring the same woman in multiple high-fashion poses. It specifies the outfit (black mini dress, thigh-high stockings, blazer), lighting (high-key studio), and requires a reference image for exact facial identity preservation.', 'Create a realistic high-fashion studio photo collage featuring the same woman in six to eight different poses, using the uploaded face image as the exact facial reference (same facial structure, eyes, nose, lips, skin tone, and overall identity).

