VALUES ('Compilation of 18 Nano Banana Pro Prompts (Tennen''s Prompt Festival)', 'A comprehensive list of 18 specialized Nano Banana Pro prompts created by the user ''Tennen,'' covering various use cases from adding Scouters and ''Super Transformation'' effects to generating retro RPG status screens, figure product layouts, and special move sequences (Kamehameha/Final Flash style).', '１．スカウタープロンプト
