VALUES ('1980s Analog New Year''s Eve Portrait Prompt', 'A detailed prompt for generating a hyper-realistic 1980s analog photograph of a woman celebrating New Year''s Eve 2026. It enforces zero alteration of the subject''s facial identity (PersonaFusion-vX.03 protocol) and specifies the aesthetic details: Kodak Gold 200 film stock, harsh on-camera flash, a royal blue velvet cocktail dress with shoulder pads, 80s volume hair, and a Y2K photo look with visible film grain and cracks.', 'Initiate PersonaFusion-vX.03 protocol: Use the exact facial identity taken from the attached reference image (or from the user’s provided face) with zero alteration.  A hyper-realistic 1980s analog photograph capturing the celebratory optimism of a New Year''s Eve studio portrait, imbued with a nostalgic, warm, and slightly formal mood, as if pulled from a family album. The image is rendered with the distinct characteristics of Kodak Gold 200 film stock, displaying warm, amber skin tones, slightly muted colors, and visible, organic film grain throughout. Illumination comes from a harsh, direct on-camera flash, creating a distinct bloom, sharp shadows, and a subtle red-eye effect. A smiling woman is confidently posed, seated with legs crossed on chunky, somewhat crudely gold-painted plywood numbers spelling out "{argument name="year" default="2026"}." She wears a shimmering royal blue stretch velvet cocktail dress, featuring pronounced shoulder pads that create a powerful, angular silhouette, a deep V-neckline, and full, gathered sleeves, cinched at the waist with a wide, self-fabric belt. Her makeup is subtly 80s chic, with a soft wash of frosted lavender eyeshadow across her lids, a precise sweep of rosy-peach blush applied high on the cheekbones, and lips defined by a coral rose lipstick with a satin finish. Her hair is a testament to 80s volume: heavily teased at the crown for maximum height, with feathered sides swept back and away from her face, and voluminous, side-swept bangs, all held in place with a visible hairspray sheen. The background is a textured studio backdrop, mottled in shades of deep teal and dusty rose, creating an abstract, dreamlike pattern, subtly lit from behind by the soft, yellow-orange glow of a "Happy New Year" neon sign.
The image is shot with a flash-lit camera, creating harsh lighting that illuminates the subject''s skin. The overall aesthetic is that of a digital camera from the year 2000, with a distinct Y2K photo look. Slightly grainy, with off white thin border and a prominent cracks and fold depicting an authentic old photograph in the 1980''s and a visible dust and scratches.', 'Nano Banana Pro', '{"Nano Banana", "Imported", "CSV"}', '{"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G9KzcNGaMAIBeGE.jpg"}', '{"sourceLink": "https://x.com/SimplyAnnisa/status/2004862084916674752", "sourcePublishedAt": "2025-12-27T10:29:04.000Z", "author": "{\"name\":\"Anissa\",\"link\":\"https://x.com/SimplyAnnisa\"}", "imported_from": "csv_batch_20260128"}')
