Extremely close to the camera lens, a tall, unadorned fir tree with exceptionally fluffy, dense branches fills the edges of the frame. The tree''s soft, out-of-locus greenery creates an intimate frame around her lace and upper body, emphasizing the shallow depth of field.

The background is a completely blurred, dreamy wash of snowy pines and a pale grey sky, with no structural elements visible. The composition is dominated by the woman''s upper body and the soft foreground elements.

