}', 'Nano Banana Pro', '{"Nano Banana", "Imported", "CSV"}', '{"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G87wzhdX0AASPfR.jpg"}', '{"sourceLink": "https://x.com/key_alvesl/status/2003803783256551717", "sourcePublishedAt": "2025-12-24T12:23:45.000Z", "author": "{\"name\":\"Key Alves\",\"link\":\"https://x.com/key_alvesl\"}", "imported_from": "csv_batch_20260128"}')
