Output: ONE image, high-fidelity transformation.
</instruction>', 'Nano Banana Pro', '{"Nano Banana", "Imported", "CSV"}', '{"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G80jZ9mXUAA21iT.jpg","https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G80kPLAXQAAGGtW.jpg"}', '{"sourceLink": "https://x.com/Gdgtify/status/2003784719893475830", "sourcePublishedAt": "2025-12-24T11:08:00.000Z", "author": "{\"name\":\"Gadgetify\",\"link\":\"https://x.com/Gdgtify\"}", "imported_from": "csv_batch_20260128"}')
