VALUES ('Advanced Commercial Food/Product Poster Template with Vertical Layering', 'A highly advanced, structured prompt template for Nano Banana Pro (intended for use with Gemini) to create high-end commercial posters for food or products. The prompt uses a ''vertical layered suspension structure'' to deconstruct the subject into components (ingredients, structure, final product) and includes detailed instructions for typography, lighting, material texture, and branding elements, all floating against a pure black background.', '画面比例：9:16 竖版
