VALUES ('Floating Sky Castle Digital Art Poster Prompt', 'A highly detailed prompt for generating a cinematic digital art poster of a majestic floating ''Sky Castle'' that fuses Western medieval architecture with subtle Qing Dynasty Chinese influences, hovering above an ethereal cloud sea rendered in ink wash style.', 'A cinematic digital art poster featuring a majestic floating "Sky Castle" in the form of a miniature island, hovering serenely above an endless sea of clouds and dominating the composition.

