VALUES ('Four-Panel Emotion Grid Generator (Joy, Anger, Sadness, Fun)', 'A detailed prompt for Nano Banana Pro to automatically generate a four-panel composition (2x2 grid) showing a consistent character (based on an uploaded image) expressing four different emotions: Joy, Anger, Sadness, and Fun. It specifies camera angles, expressions, body language, and lighting for each panel while maintaining identity consistency.', 'Using the uploaded reference image, generate a four-panel composition (upper-left, upper-right, lower-left, lower-right).

