VALUES ('Wintry Cinematic Selfie Prompt (Identity Locked)', 'A highly descriptive prompt for Gemini Nano Banana Pro to generate an ultra-realistic cinematic photograph with a film-still aesthetic. It requires strict facial likeness preservation from a reference photo, depicting a woman in a fur coat holding a glass of red wine, captured in a low-angle selfie against a snowy wooden mountain chalet background.', 'Create an ultra-realistic cinematic photograph in a film-still aesthetic, based strictly on the face from the provided reference photo, preserving 100% facial likeness with absolutely no changes to facial structure or hair.
