INSERT INTO cinematic_prompts (title, description, prompt_text, category, tags, image_urls, metadata)
VALUES ('Kamehameha Attack Image Generation (Technical Prompt)', 'A highly detailed, technical prompt structure for Nano Banana Pro (v1.2) designed to generate an image of a character charging an energy attack (Kamehameha), focusing heavily on technical specifications like camera angles, lighting, visual effects (plasma energy ball, lens flare), and precise coordinate placement for manga-style speech bubbles (''か...め...は...め...''). The user compares this technical approach (their own) to a more narrative/script-based approach (borrowed prompt).', '# Image Generation Prompt: Nano Banana Pro v1.2
# 1. 基本命令
- Task: 画像生成
- Reference: 添付画像のキャラクター、服装、画像のテイストを忠実に再現・保持する
- Quality: 超高精細 (Super High Definition)

# 2. 技術仕様
- Aspect Ratio: 16:9
- Rendering Style: 添付画像のテイストをベースに、セルシェーディング ＋ ボリュームライティングを適用
